---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { MapPin, Briefcase, GraduationCap, Award } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me - Portfolio">
  <div class="container py-16 md:py-24 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="lead">
        I'm a passionate full-stack developer with a strong focus on building scalable backend systems 
        and implementing robust DevOps practices. With over 5 years of experience in the industry, 
        I've worked on various projects ranging from microservices architectures to cloud-native applications.
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8 not-prose">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <Briefcase class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Current Position</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Senior Backend Developer at TechCorp</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <MapPin class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Location</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">San Francisco, CA</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <GraduationCap class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Education</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">B.S. Computer Science, Stanford University</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <Award class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Certifications</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">AWS Solutions Architect, CKA</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2>My Journey</h2>
      <p>
        My journey in software development began during my university years when I discovered 
        my passion for solving complex problems through code. What started as simple web 
        applications quickly evolved into a deep interest in distributed systems and cloud architecture.
      </p>
      
      <h2>What I Do</h2>
      <p>
        I specialize in designing and implementing scalable backend services using modern 
        technologies like Spring Boot, Node.js, and various cloud platforms. My expertise 
        extends to:
      </p>
      
      <ul>
        <li>Building microservices architectures that can handle millions of requests</li>
        <li>Implementing CI/CD pipelines for automated deployment and testing</li>
        <li>Optimizing database performance and designing efficient data models</li>
        <li>Setting up monitoring and alerting systems for production applications</li>
        <li>Mentoring junior developers and conducting code reviews</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Beyond Code</h2>
      <p>
        When I'm not coding, you can find me contributing to open-source projects, writing 
        technical blog posts, or exploring the latest trends in cloud computing and DevOps. 
        I believe in continuous learning and regularly attend tech conferences and workshops 
        to stay updated with industry best practices.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
      <p>
        I'm always interested in discussing new projects, innovative ideas, or opportunities 
        to collaborate. Feel free to reach out through any of the channels listed on this site.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-12 flex gap-4">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary px-6 py-3">
        Get In Touch
      </a>
      <a href="/cv" class="btn btn-secondary px-6 py-3">
        View My CV
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>